{"tid":1379723,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【MV】墳頭爛了碑  唏呀唏呀唏 (原曲: 皆大歡喜)","createTime":"2019-07-29T00:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T00:54:53.000Z","uid":236333,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed9075bf5630dadda8150c026f14c3b46361c3e","tid":1379723,"uid":236333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:01:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gx4GOnW0RJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgx4GOnW0RJs&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=fa8507f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gx4GOnW0RJs</a><br />\n<br />\n墳頭爛了碑<br />\n原曲: 皆大歡喜<br />\n改詞: 搞老母後面, 三毛語錄, Mon撚夠我未?<br />\n<br />\n為著佢媽媽進萬尺高山<br />\n破墓碑竟歡欣世間<br />\n為問佢媽怎會垃圾都生<br />\n萬眾齊心 來爆石䃹<br />\n唏呀唏呀唏何～唏 唏呀唏呀唏何～唏<br />\n<br />\n深山中 齊齊覓墓不應該<br />\n又笑又衰 民怨牽涉數代<br />\n<br />\n墳頭爛了碑唏呀唏呀唏<br />\n何氏宗親冇落塵地<br />\n個個亦賀佢今日 死咗老母毀咗碑<br />\n墳頭沒有碑君堯悲呀悲<br />\n何事分享老豆墳地<br />\n笑與淚在你我之間<br />\n爸爸都升起<br />\n<br />\n若是你將雙老埋葬沙灘<br />\n這墓碑今天不會翻<br />\n伴著你雙親快回到陰間<br />\n民意難反 待翻刀山<br />\n南～阿彌阿彌阿彌 南～阿彌阿彌阿彌<br />\n深山中 齊齊鑿墓真碑衰<br />\n是你活該 累母親有意外<br />\n<br />\n墳頭爛了碑唏呀唏呀唏<br />\n何氏宗親冇落塵地<br />\n個個亦賀佢今日 死咗老母毀咗碑<br />\n墳頭沒有碑君堯悲呀悲<br />\n何事搞親老豆墳地<br />\n笑與淚在你我之間<br />\n媽媽都升起<br />\n<br />\n碑啊碑啊悲啊悲啊悲<br />\n何父親今鋪真痛碑<br />\n過世後仍霸佔官地<br />\n鞠翻個躬君Ok<br />\n碑啊碑啊悲啊悲啊悲<br />\n何氏親生母都痛碑<br />\n悔疚舊時快慰之間<br />\n神早該吞了你"},{"pid":"13d5477574a85b6fcbdcc684203f9e0f9ba6ec9b","tid":1379723,"uid":156632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足</span></span> <br />\n大家緊記宗旨唔好被輕易帶動! <br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e545049c56be8a91ad71fd90d51b471293b67b7","tid":1379723,"uid":274180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拍枱果下笑到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e316fb2cccb4350b7b3f1178055c87d3989b55d8","tid":1379723,"uid":201178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"君堯十字步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad8b1eb294ae427c54960c4506eadd5bd9f1dfe","tid":1379723,"uid":274180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e316fb2cccb4350b7b3f1178055c87d3989b55d8","tid":1379723,"uid":201178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"君堯十字步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:42:58.000Z","msg":"屌好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1492d81219e061140371dc91d0558feea7b96bd7","tid":1379723,"uid":274180,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:32:43.000Z","msg":"呢幾日香港人都好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝樓主 好耐冇笑過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nyoutube打連登/改歌都係search唔到你啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578e32c94e91f6f47dd76ca82e175ffc348f5b5e","t